Package net.beadsproject.beads.analysis

Provides a set of classes for performing audio analysis on a stream of audio data.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
FeatureExtractor FeatureExtractor is an abstract base class for classes that perform some kind of analysis on audio data.
FeatureFrame A FeatureFrame stores a set of features for a single chunk of audio data.
FeatureLayer Stores a set of features associated with a continuous period of audio data.
SampleAnalyser SampleAnalyser handles feature analysis of a Sample.
Segmenter A Segmenter is an abstract base class for classes that divide a stream of audio data into segments.
 

Package net.beadsproject.beads.analysis Description

Provides a set of classes for performing audio analysis on a stream of audio data.
